https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Additive_smoothing
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Support_vector_machine
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/K-nearest_neighbors_algorithm
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine_learning
